Description:
Agreement with Credit
  Suisse/First Boston dated 2/6/2004 whereby the Portfolio will receive 2.45%
  per year times the notional amount. The Portfolio makes a payment only upon a
  default event on underlying loan assets (47 in total, each representing 2.13%
  of the notional value of the swap).

Agreement with
  Credit Suisse/First Boston dated 2/12/2004 whereby the Portfolio will receive
  2.45% per year times the notional amount. The Portfolio makes a payment only
  upon a default event on underlying loan assets (47 in total, each
  representing 2.13% of the notional value of the swap).

Agreement with
  Lehman Brothers dated 3/2/2005 whereby the Portfolio will receive 1.85% per
  year times the notional amount. The Portfolio makes a payment of the notional
  amount only upon a default event on the reference entity, a Revolving Credit
  Agreement issued by Syniverse Technologies, Inc.
